00:18:20.470 --> 00:18:21.545 align:middle line:90%
no exceptions.

00:18:21.545 --> 00:18:23.420 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I happen to
agree with you on that.

00:18:23.420 --> 00:18:25.330 align:middle line:84%
