if we can't experience,
in ourselves,

00:18:51.070 --> 00:18:52.600 align:middle line:90%
what those virtues are.

00:18:52.600 --> 00:18:57.010 align:middle line:84%
Such as, as you say, beauty,
truth, courage, kindness,

00:18:57.010 --> 00:18:58.780 align:middle line:90%
generosity, compassion.

