Something very striking
will happen to them.

00:19:47.050 --> 00:19:49.270 align:middle line:84%
And they'll say, this is
the universe speaking to me.

00:19:49.270 --> 00:19:51.320 align:middle line:90%
Not necessarily God, though.

00:19:51.320 --> 00:19:52.120 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:19:52.120 --> 00:19:53.830 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: Not
necessarily goodness.

00:19:53.830 --> 00:19:57.025 align:middle line:84%
So don't confuse phenomena
with spiritual truth.

00:19:57.025 --> 00:19:57.900 align:middle line:90%
They're not the same.

00:19:57.900 --> 00:19:58.890 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:19:58.890 --> 00:19:59.690 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:19:59.690 --> 00:20:02.170 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: I say that across
the board, not to you.

00:20:02.170 --> 00:20:04.080 align:middle line:84%
I think you probably
know the difference.

00:20:04.080 --> 00:20:05.050 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I understand
what you're saying.

00:20:05.050 --> 00:20:06.790 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: But you know, as
we move around in the world,

00:20:06.790 --> 00:20:08.195 align:middle line:90%
a lot of people don't get that.

00:20:08.195 --> 00:20:09.820 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people
listening to this show,

00:20:09.820 --> 00:20:12.540 align:middle line:84%
I think it's a little bit
of a different audience.

00:20:12.540 --> 00:20:14.110 align:middle line:84%
They'll appreciate
this much more.

00:20:14.110 --> 00:20:17.395 align:middle line:84%
But in mainstream society,
those things are unknown.

00:20:17.395 --> 00:20:18.520 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: They are unknown.

00:20:18.520 --> 00:20:22.330 align:middle line:84%
And so there, to me, we
have to look at, as you say,

00:20:22.330 --> 00:20:24.730 align:middle line:84%
the bad guys or the
good guys, right?

00:20:24.730 --> 00:20:29.020 align:middle line:84%
We need to look at the
greater picture of the realms

00:20:29.020 --> 00:20:30.580 align:middle line:90%
beyond the Earth plane.

00:20:30.580 --> 00:20:35.380 align:middle line:84%
At least sandwich out one
plane up and one plane down,

00:20:35.380 --> 00:20:39.250 align:middle line:84%
that we are sandwiched between
dimensions of refinement

00:20:39.250 --> 00:20:42.530 align:middle line:84%
and less refinement--
lighter and darker.

00:20:42.530 --> 00:20:45.940 align:middle line:84%
And so if these realms
and the beings within them

00:20:45.940 --> 00:20:50.050 align:middle line:84%
can permeate into
this realm, and begin

00:20:50.050 --> 00:20:54.160 align:middle line:84%
influencing, demanding,
interfering, even giving

00:20:54.160 --> 00:20:56.560 align:middle line:90%
lovely guidance and such.

00:20:56.560 --> 00:20:58.750 align:middle line:84%
We're never alone
because we are depending

00:20:58.750 --> 00:21:00.040 align:middle line:90%
on our own field of resonance.

00:21:00.040 --> 00:21:01.780 align:middle line:84%
We are always being
influenced also

00:21:01.780 --> 00:21:03.260 align:middle line:84%
from these higher
and lower realms.

00:21:03.260 --> 00:21:04.060 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Agreed.

00:21:04.060 --> 00:21:05.935 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Can you talk
about that whole dance

00:21:05.935 --> 00:21:07.840 align:middle line:84%
and share with people,
even viscerally,

00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:08.950 align:middle line:90%
what that looks like?

00:21:08.950 --> 00:21:12.110 align:middle line:84%
And you can use outlandish
language if you wish to.

00:21:12.110 --> 00:21:12.910 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Good.

00:21:12.910 --> 00:21:13.960 align:middle line:90%
I like to hear that.

00:21:13.960 --> 00:21:14.760 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:21:14.760 --> 00:21:16.630 align:middle line:84%
Because it's important
we understand

00:21:16.630 --> 00:21:18.160 align:middle line:90%
we're being influenced by both.

00:21:18.160 --> 00:21:18.970 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Yeah.

00:21:18.970 --> 00:21:21.400 align:middle line:84%
The key thing to
see here, for me,

00:21:21.400 --> 00:21:26.230 align:middle line:84%
is that free will and
the absolute sovereignty

00:21:26.230 --> 00:21:30.070 align:middle line:84%
of the individual's
decision-making process.

00:21:30.070 --> 00:21:32.650 align:middle line:84%
To know good and evil, to
know right and wrong, to know

00:21:32.650 --> 00:21:35.380 align:middle line:90%
truth and falsehood is primary.

00:21:35.380 --> 00:21:40.990 align:middle line:84%
All the time, there are positive
disembodied supernatural

00:21:40.990 --> 00:21:46.840 align:middle line:84%
entities trying to promote
discernment and positive

00:21:46.840 --> 00:21:49.030 align:middle line:90%
excellent discrimination.

00:21:49.030 --> 00:21:51.730 align:middle line:84%
An undiscriminating
human is about human.

00:21:51.730 --> 00:21:56.270 align:middle line:84%
You want discriminating,
discerning, knowledgeable,

00:21:56.270 --> 00:21:58.500 align:middle line:90%
wise, judgmental humans.

00:21:58.500 --> 00:22:01.280 align:middle line:84%
Judgment-- if you can't
judge, you'll be dead.

00:22:01.280 --> 00:22:04.780 align:middle line:84%
If I can't judge to cross the
road if it's safe, I'm dead.

00:22:04.780 --> 00:22:07.040 align:middle line:84%
If I can't judge a good
person from a bad person,

00:22:07.040 --> 00:22:08.150 align:middle line:90%
I'm in trouble.

00:22:08.150 --> 00:22:11.680 align:middle line:84%
So you want discrimination
judgment, discernment, knowing.

00:22:11.680 --> 00:22:15.790 align:middle line:84%
There are negative disembodied
supernatural entities-- real,

00:22:15.790 --> 00:22:17.290 align:middle line:90%
very real--

00:22:17.290 --> 00:22:21.680 align:middle line:84%
who want the opposite of that,
who want you to not judge,

00:22:21.680 --> 00:22:22.660 align:middle line:90%
not discriminate.

00:22:22.660 --> 00:22:24.310 align:middle line:84%
And you can see
the parallels there

00:22:24.310 --> 00:22:26.210 align:middle line:84%
in mainstream culture
at the moment.

00:22:26.210 --> 00:22:27.520 align:middle line:90%
Don't be judgmental.

00:22:27.520 --> 00:22:30.770 align:middle line:90%
Don't discriminate.

00:22:30.770 --> 00:22:34.000 align:middle line:84%
They don't want you
to see absolutes,

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.140 align:middle line:90%
that everything's relative.

00:22:35.140 --> 00:22:39.190 align:middle line:84%
It's all about, essentially,
human ethics and laws that ebb

00:22:39.190 --> 00:22:41.290 align:middle line:90%
and flow over the millennia.

00:22:41.290 --> 00:22:42.670 align:middle line:90%
That's wrong.

00:22:42.670 --> 00:22:46.540 align:middle line:84%
That's demonic influence,
no question about it.

00:22:46.540 --> 00:22:48.320 align:middle line:84%
I don't like to talk
about that a ton,

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:50.540 align:middle line:84%
because I like to put the
power where it belongs,

00:22:50.540 --> 00:22:53.290 align:middle line:84%
which is a God-given
power in free will, which

00:22:53.290 --> 00:22:57.010 align:middle line:84%
all those entities-- strangely
enough-- have to respect.

00:22:57.010 --> 00:23:00.760 align:middle line:84%
What the negative demonic
powers do, which-- again,

00:23:00.760 --> 00:23:03.010 align:middle line:84%
I emphasize that I'm not
speaking figuratively,

00:23:03.010 --> 00:23:06.010 align:middle line:84%
I mean literally--
what they want to do

00:23:06.010 --> 00:23:09.320 align:middle line:84%
is persuade you to
give your power away.

00:23:09.320 --> 00:23:11.830 align:middle line:84%
It's a little bit like the
mythology of a vampire.

00:23:11.830 --> 00:23:14.632 align:middle line:84%
