00:23:38.050 --> 00:23:41.980 align:middle line:84%
So the only power that
empire, the administration

00:23:41.980 --> 00:23:44.920 align:middle line:84%
of that supernatural
force, and the supernatural

00:23:44.920 --> 00:23:46.300 align:middle line:90%
forces themselves have--

00:23:46.300 --> 00:23:48.940 align:middle line:84%
the only power they
have is the trick

00:23:48.940 --> 00:23:53.650 align:middle line:84%
to get you to give your
consent to their naughtiness.

00:23:53.650 --> 00:23:54.680 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Indeed.

