The beauty of a sunset, the
beauty of a lover's face,

00:27:10.850 --> 00:27:13.340 align:middle line:84%
the beauty of form
and proportion,

00:27:13.340 --> 00:27:14.500 align:middle line:90%
the beauty of color.

00:27:14.500 --> 00:27:15.890 align:middle line:90%
They're universal.

00:27:15.890 --> 00:27:19.010 align:middle line:10%
You can show people anywhere
in the world a beautiful thing

00:27:19.010 --> 00:27:20.090 align:middle line:10%
and they'll see it.

00:27:20.090 --> 00:27:22.310 align:middle line:10%
As long as you remove the
cultural obstructions away,

00:27:22.310 --> 00:27:22.970 align:middle line:10%
they can see it.

00:27:22.970 --> 00:27:24.012 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, exactly.

00:27:24.012 --> 00:27:26.810 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: So let let's play
a game for a minute, right?

00:27:26.810 --> 00:27:29.700 align:middle line:84%
Let's say there's
a God, good guy.

00:27:29.700 --> 00:27:30.500 align:middle line:90%
And he says--

00:27:30.500 --> 00:27:31.500 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Or good woman.

00:27:31.500 --> 00:27:33.230 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Or, good woman.

00:27:33.230 --> 00:27:35.910 align:middle line:84%
Well, there is a
reason why it's male

00:27:35.910 --> 00:27:38.270 align:middle line:84%
but I will get to that
another time-- an entity.

00:27:38.270 --> 00:27:43.650 align:middle line:84%
God is there and he says,
OK, the game is come find me,

00:27:43.650 --> 00:27:47.670 align:middle line:84%
Right there's another guy
that he actually made, Satan,

00:27:47.670 --> 00:27:48.470 align:middle line:90%
and he says, OK.

00:27:48.470 --> 00:27:49.678 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to play a game too.

00:27:49.678 --> 00:27:51.920 align:middle line:84%
And I've been asked
to play this role.

00:27:51.920 --> 00:27:55.730 align:middle line:84%
My rules are there's
nothing to find.

00:27:55.730 --> 00:27:58.160 align:middle line:90%
Forget it.

00:27:58.160 --> 00:28:00.210 align:middle line:84%
That is, if you're
teaching children--

00:28:00.210 --> 00:28:01.880 align:middle line:90%
which I do at times--

00:28:01.880 --> 00:28:02.990 align:middle line:90%
that's the game.

00:28:02.990 --> 00:28:04.430 align:middle line:90%
God's like, come find me.

00:28:04.430 --> 00:28:07.610 align:middle line:84%
Because this is a supernatural
amazing adventure for real.

00:28:07.610 --> 00:28:10.807 align:middle line:84%
Not joking, not
figurative language here.

00:28:10.807 --> 00:28:12.140 align:middle line:90%
We're not speaking symbolically.

00:28:12.140 --> 00:28:13.130 align:middle line:90%
Real.

00:28:13.130 --> 00:28:17.300 align:middle line:84%
And Satan's job, made by God
as part of that same test,

00:28:17.300 --> 00:28:19.230 align:middle line:84%
is to say, there's
nothing to find.

00:28:19.230 --> 00:28:20.030 align:middle line:90%
Forget it.

00:28:20.030 --> 00:28:21.410 align:middle line:90%
Are you serious?

00:28:21.410 --> 00:28:22.580 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing here, folks.

00:28:22.580 --> 00:28:23.750 align:middle line:90%
It's DNA.

00:28:23.750 --> 00:28:25.000 align:middle line:90%
It's an empty vacuum of space.

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:25.875 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing here.

00:28:25.875 --> 00:28:26.805 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Make it up.

00:28:26.805 --> 00:28:27.930 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: It's just humans.

00:28:27.930 --> 00:28:29.100 align:middle line:90%
We're the top of the tree.

00:28:29.100 --> 00:28:30.320 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing.

00:28:30.320 --> 00:28:32.120 align:middle line:90%
That is the game.

00:28:32.120 --> 00:28:35.570 align:middle line:84%
All mainstream imperial
media across Europe,

00:28:35.570 --> 00:28:38.060 align:middle line:84%
in particular, Africa,
Asia, and America

00:28:38.060 --> 00:28:40.850 align:middle line:84%
too-- although America is
much freer, I'm glad to say.

00:28:40.850 --> 00:28:44.750 align:middle line:84%
All imperial media is
tipped in this direction

00:28:44.750 --> 00:28:47.870 align:middle line:84%
to say there's nothing
to find, all of it.

00:28:47.870 --> 00:28:51.560 align:middle line:84%
Beauty shows you there's
something to find.

00:28:51.560 --> 00:28:54.630 align:middle line:84%
Truth shows you there's
something to find.

00:28:54.630 --> 00:28:58.310 align:middle line:84%
Because the deeper you pursue
it, you realize it was made.

00:28:58.310 --> 00:28:59.660 align:middle line:90%
That beauty was made.

00:28:59.660 --> 00:29:01.550 align:middle line:84%
It didn't just
evolve out of carbon.

00:29:01.550 --> 00:29:03.050 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It rose
as a happenstance.

00:29:03.050 --> 00:29:04.940 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: It didn't just
evolve of, you know,

00:29:04.940 --> 00:29:08.270 align:middle line:84%
nitrogen and hydrogen and
snot crawling out of an ocean.

00:29:08.270 --> 00:29:09.070 align:middle line:90%
It didn't.

00:29:09.070 --> 00:29:09.870 align:middle line:90%
That's garbage.

00:29:09.870 --> 00:29:11.970 align:middle line:90%
That evolution is garbage.

00:29:11.970 --> 00:29:12.950 align:middle line:90%
It was made.

00:29:12.950 --> 00:29:14.310 align:middle line:90%
It was designed.

00:29:14.310 --> 00:29:15.860 align:middle line:90%
It's grace and elegance.

00:29:15.860 --> 00:29:16.860 align:middle line:90%
It's a gift.

00:29:16.860 --> 00:29:19.790 align:middle line:84%
It's an invitation
to know divinity.

00:29:19.790 --> 00:29:22.740 align:middle line:84%
And all you've got to do is
trust your instincts on that.

00:29:22.740 --> 00:29:25.400 align:middle line:84%
Examine the good
scripture on that.

00:29:25.400 --> 00:29:27.230 align:middle line:84%
Speak to wise men
and women you can

00:29:27.230 --> 00:29:29.840 align:middle line:84%
locate with a beating
heart in this world.

00:29:29.840 --> 00:29:31.970 align:middle line:84%
They will all agree
on that, all of them.

00:29:31.970 --> 00:29:34.730 align:middle line:84%
But still, the truth is always
yours-- primarily is yours.

00:29:34.730 --> 00:29:38.330 align:middle line:84%
But as you do that, it
will lead you to reality.

00:29:38.330 --> 00:29:41.820 align:middle line:84%
This negative game
leads you away.

00:29:41.820 --> 00:29:45.080 align:middle line:84%
Now that game, like
every game, is finite.

00:29:45.080 --> 00:29:47.670 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't go on for millions
of years forever and ever.

00:29:47.670 --> 00:29:48.470 align:middle line:90%
It's finite.

00:29:48.470 --> 00:29:49.730 align:middle line:90%
And you know what?

00:29:49.730 --> 00:29:51.650 align:middle line:90%
It's coming to its conclusion.

00:29:51.650 --> 00:29:54.470 align:middle line:84%
There's not a lot of
that game left now.

00:29:54.470 --> 00:29:55.850 align:middle line:90%
Again, why can we say this?

00:29:55.850 --> 00:29:59.720 align:middle line:90%
Because it's in your face now.

00:29:59.720 --> 00:30:02.090 align:middle line:84%
The guy, the good guy,
God is saying, OK, guys.

00:30:02.090 --> 00:30:04.320 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to make this
really, really easy for you.

00:30:04.320 --> 00:30:07.340 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to give you so
much incredibly obvious

00:30:07.340 --> 00:30:11.600 align:middle line:84%
good and evil in your face,
you'll have to make a decision.

00:30:11.600 --> 00:30:15.530 align:middle line:84%
You'll be impelled from within
and compelled from without

00:30:15.530 --> 00:30:16.678 align:middle line:90%
to make a decision.

00:30:16.678 --> 00:30:18.220 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to
make it really easy.

00:30:18.220 --> 00:30:18.610 align:middle line:90%
Because you know what?

00:30:18.610 --> 00:30:20.110 align:middle line:90%
I'm wrapping this up soon.

00:30:20.110 --> 00:30:21.790 align:middle line:90%
This is finished soon.

00:30:21.790 --> 00:30:24.490 align:middle line:84%
And only those of you who have
taken the time and trouble

00:30:24.490 --> 00:30:28.180 align:middle line:84%
to discern what is
real will come with me.

00:30:28.180 --> 00:30:31.570 align:middle line:84%
Everything else will be
completely deleted forever.

00:30:31.570 --> 00:30:36.280 align:middle line:84%
The entire 3D superstructure
gone forever, gone.

00:30:36.280 --> 00:30:40.090 align:middle line:84%
That's the proposition
that I put forward to you.

00:30:40.090 --> 00:30:42.700 align:middle line:84%
And with each
passing minute, I'm

00:30:42.700 --> 00:30:44.900 align:middle line:84%
more literal in how
I feel about that.

00:30:44.900 --> 00:30:45.700 align:middle line:90%
I'm not joking.

00:30:45.700 --> 00:30:46.850 align:middle line:90%
It's not figurative.

00:30:46.850 --> 00:30:47.170 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:30:47.170 --> 00:30:47.620 align:middle line:90%
I know you are.

00:30:47.620 --> 00:30:48.800 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: I can feel it.

00:30:48.800 --> 00:30:50.020 align:middle line:90%
I can feel it all my life.

00:30:50.020 --> 00:30:52.300 align:middle line:84%
And it's getting
faster and deeper.

00:30:52.300 --> 00:30:55.780 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I feel this
is a critical time

00:30:55.780 --> 00:30:57.880 align:middle line:84%
in human consciousness
to make that shift.

00:30:57.880 --> 00:30:58.780 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: It is.

00:30:58.780 --> 00:31:02.180 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: In terms of the end
of the 3D reality, I don't know.

00:31:02.180 --> 00:31:03.700 align:middle line:90%
I have no idea.

00:31:03.700 --> 00:31:06.130 align:middle line:84%
But in terms of the
absolute necessity

00:31:06.130 --> 00:31:08.230 align:middle line:84%
to start making these
leaps in consciousness,

00:31:08.230 --> 00:31:11.650 align:middle line:84%
I feel it in my cells as
well, toward whatever end

00:31:11.650 --> 00:31:12.670 align:middle line:90%
that might be.

00:31:12.670 --> 00:31:14.590 align:middle line:84%
And just to go back
for a moment, for any

00:31:14.590 --> 00:31:17.140 align:middle line:84%
of the women in particular
watching, what you mean

00:31:17.140 --> 00:31:19.570 align:middle line:84%
God's automatically
a male, you know,

00:31:19.570 --> 00:31:20.890 align:middle line:90%
and the creator is a male?

00:31:20.890 --> 00:31:22.180 align:middle line:90%
I just want to offer this.

00:31:22.180 --> 00:31:25.390 align:middle line:84%
If you're looking at it through
a lens of ancient gnostics,

00:31:25.390 --> 00:31:27.010 align:middle line:84%
you would say first
was the logos.

00:31:27.010 --> 00:31:29.020 align:middle line:84%
That's simply the
thought, right?

00:31:29.020 --> 00:31:30.570 align:middle line:84%
The thought, the
creative thought.

00:31:30.570 --> 00:31:33.730 align:middle line:84%
Then the prima material
absorbs the thought

00:31:33.730 --> 00:31:34.990 align:middle line:90%
and then makes manifest.

00:31:34.990 --> 00:31:37.600 align:middle line:84%
The male and female
work in perfect symmetry

00:31:37.600 --> 00:31:38.990 align:middle line:90%
and companionship together.

00:31:38.990 --> 00:31:43.120 align:middle line:84%
So in my understanding,
you have the logos,

00:31:43.120 --> 00:31:45.520 align:middle line:84%
the thought which is
classified as male

00:31:45.520 --> 00:31:46.670 align:middle line:90%
in all ancient traditions--

00:31:46.670 --> 00:31:47.628 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Like the sun.

00:31:47.628 --> 00:31:49.510 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Like the sun, exactly.

00:31:49.510 --> 00:31:52.205 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: And it's birthed
in life, which is female.

00:31:52.205 --> 00:31:53.830 align:middle line:84%
The two characters
without each other--

00:31:53.830 --> 00:31:55.090 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The life is all
expressed through the female

00:31:55.090 --> 00:31:56.080 align:middle line:90%
and the feminine.

00:31:56.080 --> 00:31:56.440 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Yeah, agreed.

00:31:56.440 --> 00:31:57.020 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So there we go.

00:31:57.020 --> 00:31:58.615 align:middle line:84%
So let's just say
that is a companion

00:31:58.615 --> 00:32:00.055 align:middle line:90%
shift that is beautiful.

00:32:00.055 --> 00:32:00.370 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: You're very kind.

00:32:00.370 --> 00:32:01.446 align:middle line:90%
You're very kind.

00:32:01.446 --> 00:32:03.860 align:middle line:84%
You're very kind to these
watchers and viewers,

00:32:03.860 --> 00:32:04.720 align:middle line:90%
aren't you?

00:32:04.720 --> 00:32:05.530 align:middle line:90%
How nice you are.

00:32:05.530 --> 00:32:06.640 align:middle line:90%
I wouldn't have bothered.

00:32:06.640 --> 00:32:07.800 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I value kindness.

00:32:07.800 --> 00:32:08.730 align:middle line:90%
It is true.

00:32:08.730 --> 00:32:11.830 align:middle line:84%
So now we're going to go
into absolute good and evil.

00:32:11.830 --> 00:32:14.740 align:middle line:84%
And I just pulled this
from Nietzsche's "Beyond

00:32:14.740 --> 00:32:16.803 align:middle line:84%
Good and Evil", just
the beginning line.

00:32:16.803 --> 00:32:18.220 align:middle line:10%
There's this
beautiful poem called

00:32:18.220 --> 00:32:19.405 align:middle line:10%
"The Genius of the Heart".

00:32:19.405 --> 00:32:21.280 align:middle line:84%
And so we're only going
to share a few words.

00:32:21.280 --> 00:32:23.980 align:middle line:84%
It says, "the
genius of the heart

00:32:23.980 --> 00:32:28.600 align:middle line:84%
silences all that is
loud and self-satisfied,

00:32:28.600 --> 00:32:30.340 align:middle line:90%
teaching it to listen."

00:32:30.340 --> 00:32:32.710 align:middle line:84%
So this-- again, this
noise, this distraction,

00:32:32.710 --> 00:32:36.410 align:middle line:84%
this pulling down that
anything goes kind of message.

00:32:36.410 --> 00:32:38.920 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about
through your lens

00:32:38.920 --> 00:32:43.430 align:middle line:84%
where we begin to discern
absolute good and evil.

00:32:43.430 --> 00:32:46.660 align:middle line:84%
He's suggesting the
heart is one mechanism.

00:32:46.660 --> 00:32:49.200 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: Absolute
good is reality.

00:32:49.200 --> 00:32:51.890 align:middle line:90%
Absolute evil is unreality.

00:32:51.890 --> 00:32:52.690 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:32:52.690 --> 00:32:53.600 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: That's it.

00:32:53.600 --> 00:32:54.558 align:middle line:90%
It's as simple as that.

00:32:54.558 --> 00:32:56.430 align:middle line:90%
What is real is good.

00:32:56.430 --> 00:32:58.227 align:middle line:90%
What is unreal is bad.

00:32:58.227 --> 00:32:59.560 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Because it's delusion.

00:32:59.560 --> 00:33:00.820 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Because it's delusion.

00:33:00.820 --> 00:33:01.620 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:33:01.620 --> 00:33:04.100 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: So remember our
game, so the only game in town.

00:33:04.100 --> 00:33:04.590 align:middle line:90%
That's it.

00:33:04.590 --> 00:33:05.500 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:33:05.500 --> 00:33:07.792 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: The game is what
is real because what is real

00:33:07.792 --> 00:33:09.190 align:middle line:90%
is leading you to truth.

00:33:09.190 --> 00:33:13.360 align:middle line:84%
And that truth is your
exit from this classroom

00:33:13.360 --> 00:33:16.660 align:middle line:84%
to lead the actual adult
spiritual life that this

00:33:16.660 --> 00:33:17.650 align:middle line:90%
is preparation for.

00:33:17.650 --> 00:33:19.450 align:middle line:90%
This is our childhood.

00:33:19.450 --> 00:33:21.070 align:middle line:90%
And it's soon to end.

00:33:21.070 --> 00:33:27.070 align:middle line:84%
And when it ends, we'll
go to a new world, which

00:33:27.070 --> 00:33:30.700 align:middle line:84%
resembles this in some ways
but is without disharmony

00:33:30.700 --> 00:33:33.250 align:middle line:84%
and without the test, because
the test has been completed.

00:33:33.250 --> 00:33:35.993 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Which is classically
considered the fourth realm--

00:33:35.993 --> 00:33:36.910 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: Well, it's--

00:33:36.910 --> 00:33:38.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: --in
classical teachings.

00:33:38.170 --> 00:33:39.550 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: In
classical teachings,

00:33:39.550 --> 00:33:41.100 align:middle line:84%
I don't know which ones
you mean, but it could be.

00:33:41.100 --> 00:33:42.910 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Non-dimension
fourth realm, but go ahead.

00:33:42.910 --> 00:33:43.450 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: I see.

00:33:43.450 --> 00:33:44.920 align:middle line:84%
In my teaching,
it would be called

00:33:44.920 --> 00:33:46.360 align:middle line:90%
the new Earth, the new heavens.

00:33:46.360 --> 00:33:47.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:33:47.200 --> 00:33:48.000 align:middle line:90%
it's the same.

00:33:48.000 --> 00:33:49.292 align:middle line:90%
>>KRAMER: It could be the same.

00:33:49.292 --> 00:33:51.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Functionally
speaking, it looks the same.

00:33:51.520 --> 00:33:53.650 align:middle line:84%
>>KRAMER: Well, it's
a paradise world

00:33:53.650 --> 00:33:55.240 align:middle line:84%
which only contains
the people who've

00:33:55.240 --> 00:33:57.770 align:middle line:84%
taken the time to
discern, which frankly,

00:33:57.770 --> 00:34:01.120 align:middle line:84%
are the people that you'd want
to spend time with in paradise.

00:34:01.120 --> 00:34:03.040 align:middle line:90%
So that's a good thing.

00:34:03.040 --> 00:34:07.510 align:middle line:84%
The unreal world
here is a world of--

00:34:07.510 --> 00:34:08.889 align:middle line:90%
how can I say it--

00:34:08.889 --> 00:34:09.790 align:middle line:90%
disavowal.

00:34:09.790 --> 00:34:11.050 align:middle line:90%
A world of resignation.

00:34:11.050 --> 00:34:12.610 align:middle line:90%
A world of defeat.

00:34:12.610 --> 00:34:17.409 align:middle line:84%
A world of giving consent
to things that are wicked.

00:34:17.409 --> 00:34:20.420 align:middle line:90%
That's what creates evil.

00:34:20.420 --> 00:34:25.570 align:middle line:84%
And if you look at the word
sin, for example, in scripture,

00:34:25.570 --> 00:34:28.300 align:middle line:84%
there's 26 different
terms for that.

00:34:28.300 --> 00:34:31.270 align:middle line:84%
And they range-- I call it
the traffic lights of sin--

00:34:31.270 --> 00:34:33.130 align:middle line:84%
from a green
traffic light, which

00:34:33.130 --> 00:34:34.580 align:middle line:90%
is like you've made a mistake.

00:34:34.580 --> 00:34:36.610 align:middle line:90%
So that's a kind of sin.

00:34:36.610 --> 00:34:38.739 align:middle line:84%
And there's Hebrew and
Greek words for that.

00:34:38.739 --> 00:34:40.540 align:middle line:84%
And that's like,
you know, I thought

00:34:40.540 --> 00:34:43.100 align:middle line:90%
it was OK to eat this food.

00:34:43.100 --> 00:34:46.140 align:middle line:84%
But I realize now that
it's hurting my body.

00:34:46.140 --> 00:34:49.060 align:middle line:84%
Or, I thought it was OK
to kiss this lovely woman.

00:34:49.060 --> 00:34:52.210 align:middle line:84%
And I realize that's not a good
idea because I don't know her

00:34:52.210 --> 00:34:54.290 align:middle line:90%
well enough and it's not fair.

00:34:54.290 --> 00:34:55.090 align:middle line:90%
That's an error.

00:34:55.090 --> 00:34:58.310 align:middle line:84%
People make those errors
in life and get over it.

00:34:58.310 --> 00:34:59.990 align:middle line:90%
You make a change.

00:34:59.990 --> 00:35:00.790 align:middle line:90%
You turn.

